        Full licensing details are on the <a href="https://avs.nparks.gov.sg/pets/licensing-a-pet/information-on-dog-and-cat-licences/licensing-requirements/" class="underline underline-offset-2 text-[var(--color-accent-hover)]">AVS dog licensing requirements</a> page. You won't need to chase any of it yourself; it's handled with you at purchase. First-time owners must also complete the <a href="https://avs.nparks.gov.sg/pets/licensing-a-pet/applying-for-dog-and-cat-licences/pet-ownership-course/" class="underline underline-offset-2 text-[var(--color-accent-hover)]">free online pet ownership course</a> before licensing.
      </p>
    </div>
